version_description: No standard chord or tabs versions. Only Pro versions so far. Capo allows easier chords. Transpose up 3 steps and remove capo to play original bar chords.
Complete song with chords. An unusual song structure.

This acoustic version is tabbed from a youtube vid of Glen Tilbrook of Squeeze teaching this song to Steve Poltz. It's really worth a look as he goes through the timing for each part. Here's the link. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pEmftclneD4.
